            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the <strong>sausages</strong> and <strong>chips</strong> are almost cooked, add the <strong>brioche sub rolls</strong> to a separate baking tray&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Put the tray in the oven for 2-3 min or until warmed through</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
